{"word":"φθινύθω","slug":"φθινύθω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n110709\" key=\"fqinu/qw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">φθῐν-ύθω</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">[ῠ]</foreign>, poet. for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φθίνω,</foreign> only <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> and <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns>; <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns> <sense id=\"n110709.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φθινύθεσκε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:491\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.491</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n110709.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> trans., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">waste,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φθινύθουσιν ἔδοντες οἶκον ἐμόν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:250\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.250</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οἶνον δὲ φ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:95\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.95</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἵ μευ φ. φίλον κῆρ</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cause</tr_> it <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to pine away</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10:485\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.485</biblScope> </bibl> (so perh. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:491\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.491</biblScope> </bibl>); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἵνα μηκέτ᾽ ὀδυρομένη . . αἰῶνα φθινύθω</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">waste</tr_> my life, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:18:204\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.204</biblScope> </bibl>; in later <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μαψίδιον φ. πόνον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0024.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:186\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Opp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">C.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.186</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n110709.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> intr., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">waste away, decay, perish,</tr_> of men, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λαοὶ μὲν φ. περὶ πτόλιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:327\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.327</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:466\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.466</b